    <rdfs:comment rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">An OWL ontology for the pizza domain, built incrementally through the SULO Pizza Tutorial. Covers spatial composition, qualities, quantities, processes, information entities, time, and spatial containment.</rdfs:comment>
